growthexperiments-manage-mentors-error-n: Iphutha: Akekho umsebenzisi onjalo one-ID yomsebenzisi etjhiwoko. Lokhu mhlamunye kuliphutha langaphakathi.
growthexperiments-manage-mentors-add-men: Ngokusebenzisa iforomo leli, kungenzeka ukufaka umeluleki omutjha erherhweni. Umsebenzisi ongezelelweko akutlhogeki bona ahlangabezane nemibandela yokufaneleka. Bafakwa njengomeluleki owabelwe ngesandla, begodu bayakghona ukutjhugulula amasethingi wabo.
